  06 Apr 2008; Markus Meier <maekke@gentoo.org> ruby-opengl-0.32g.ebuild:
  amd64/x86 stable, bug #216476

*ruby-opengl-0.60.0 (06 Apr 2008)

  06 Apr 2008; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org>
  +ruby-opengl-0.60.0.ebuild:
  Version bump: upstream has changed ownership and location, switched to gem
  version for easier maintenance, dropped most keywords due to newly
  introduced dependency. Closes #201833.

  06 Apr 2008; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> ruby-opengl-0.32c.ebuild,
  ruby-opengl-0.32d.ebuild, ruby-opengl-0.32g.ebuild:
  Add missing dependencies to 32c version, fixing #216379; fix quotation of
  variables

  22 Feb 2007; Piotr Jaroszy≈Ñski <peper@gentoo.org> ChangeLog:
  Transition to Manifest2.

  12 May 2006; Caleb Tennis <caleb@gentoo.org> ruby-opengl-0.32g.ebuild:
  Don't use the sub platform trick

*ruby-opengl-0.32g (29 Apr 2006)

  29 Apr 2006; Caleb Tennis <caleb@gentoo.org> +ruby-opengl-0.32g.ebuild:
  version bump

  13 Jan 2006; Ferris McCormick <fmccor@gentoo.org>
  ruby-opengl-0.32d.ebuild:
  There are two implementations of glut (media-libs/glut, media-libs/freeglut),
  and both provide virtual/glut, both work with ruby-opengl.  Hence, depend on
  virtual/glut instead of media-libs/glut (Bug #118899).

  17 Oct 2005; Aron Griffis <agriffis@gentoo.org> ruby-opengl-0.32d.ebuild:
  Mark 0.32d stable on ia64

  03 Oct 2005; Aron Griffis <agriffis@gentoo.org> ruby-opengl-0.32d.ebuild:
  Mark 0.32d ~ia64

  09 Sep 2005; Ferris McCormick <fmccor@gentoo.org>
  ruby-opengl-0.32d.ebuild:
  Stable on sparc.  Runs with no problems.

  24 Apr 2005; Simon Stelling <blubb@gentoo.org> ruby-opengl-0.32c.ebuild,
  ruby-opengl-0.32d.ebuild:
  0.32d ~amd64, 0.32c amd64

  03 Oct 2004; Mamoru KOMACHI <usata@gentoo.org> ruby-opengl-0.32d.ebuild:
  Stable on x86, ppc and alpha.

  12 Aug 2004; Tom Martin <slarti@gentoo.org> ruby-opengl-0.32c.ebuild:
  Marked ~amd64; resolving bug 57618. Thanks to Robert Gogolok
  <robertgogolok@gmx.de> for reporting.

  05 Jul 2004; Mamoru KOMACHI <usata@gentoo.org> ruby-opengl-0.32c.ebuild,
  ruby-opengl-0.32d.ebuild:
